Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:18.90,TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:20.88,TEXT,,0,0,0,,薇薇安？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:22.20,TEXT,,0,0,0,,對
